64
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,079
Where are you going?

65
00:07:44,279 --> 00:07:45,519
To cleanse myself.

66
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,639
You must be feverish.

67
00:07:48,319 --> 00:07:49,319
The toilet's over there.

68
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,519
Perhaps

69
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:52,399
I'll take you.

70
00:07:53,959 --> 00:07:55,560
No need, young master.

71
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,680
You dared to drug Grandpa?

72
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,560
Aren't you afraid he'll punish you?

73
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:18,040
Let me finish!

74
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,639
I put laxative in his food,

75
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,319
but antidote in his medicine.

76
00:08:26,079 --> 00:08:26,879
He went at midnight,

77
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,639
so he ate but didn't take medicine.

78
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,319
Meaning?

79
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:35,519
He's faking illness.

80
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,559
Grandpa's too old

81
00:08:38,399 --> 00:08:39,360
