82
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,440
To hide something.

83
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:45,159
And he seems unfamiliar here.

84
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,519
Meaning?

85
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,000
I watched Bai Ye carefully.

86
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,279
I noticed he

87
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,399
eats and carries lanterns

88
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,159
with his right hand.

89
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,240
Grandpa's left-handed.

90
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:03,919
So he's hiding

91
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,039
to avoid contact with us.

92
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,159
To not get exposed.

93
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,159
You mean

94
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,159
my grandpa

95
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:13,120
